Reasoning: The paper discusses the use of wearable computers and video cameras to train a computer-vision system for field-geology and astrobiology. This falls under the sub-category of computer vision (cs.CV) as well as robotics (cs.RO) since the wearable computer is being used in a field setting. Additionally, the use of machine learning algorithms to train the computer-vision system falls under the sub-categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and neural networks (cs.NE).
